(392, 32, 1, '', '2018-11-28 14:06:49', 558, 6092, 'f22110fce3bf96622fc509d2c210045297eb2292', '{"id":32,"asset_id":247,"title":"Viete ako funguje face recognition technol\\u00f3gia?","alias":"viete-ako-funguje-face-recognition-technologia","introtext":"<h3 id=\\"ak\\u00e9-zmeny-prin\\u00e1\\u0161a-nov\\u00e9-nariadenie-v-oblasti-ochrany-osobn\\u00fdch-\\u00fadajov-ou-pre-firmy\\">\\u010co je to face recognition?<\\/h3>\\r\\n<p>\\u201eFace recognition\\u201c technol\\u00f3gie, je technol\\u00f3gia schopn\\u00e1 rozpozna\\u0165 a\\u00a0identifikova\\u0165 osoby z\\u00a0digit\\u00e1lnych fotografi\\u00ed a vide\\u00ed na rozpozn\\u00e1vanie tv\\u00e1r\\u00ed. Met\\u00f3d, ak\\u00fdmi tieto syst\\u00e9my funguj\\u00fa je nieko\\u013eko, ale vo v\\u0161eobecnosti v\\u00e4\\u010d\\u0161ina z\\u00a0nich pracuje na z\\u00e1klade porovn\\u00e1vania vybran\\u00fdch \\u010d\\u0155t tv\\u00e1re z dan\\u00e9ho obrazu s\\u00a0\\u010drtami tv\\u00e1re v r\\u00e1mci datab\\u00e1zy. \\u0160tandardne je t\\u00e1to technol\\u00f3gia vyu\\u017e\\u00edvan\\u00e1 v\\u00a0r\\u00e1mci bezpe\\u010dnostn\\u00fdch a\\u00a0zabezpe\\u010dovac\\u00edch syst\\u00e9mov, no s\\u00a0rast\\u00facim mno\\u017estvom smart technol\\u00f3gi\\u00ed je zrejm\\u00e9, \\u017ee vyu\\u017eitie rozpozn\\u00e1vania tv\\u00e1re bude aplikovate\\u013en\\u00e9 aj v\\u00a0in\\u00fdch oblastiach. Ot\\u00e1zkou ale ost\\u00e1va bezpe\\u010dnos\\u0165 a\\u00a0ochrana s\\u00fakromia.Mot\\u00edv, pre\\u010do nap\\u00edsa\\u0165 tento \\u010dl\\u00e1nok, bol celkom jednoduch\\u00fd. Pri bl\\u00faden\\u00ed po Amazone a\\u00a0snahe n\\u00e1js\\u0165 vec, ktor\\u00fa nutne nepotrebujem som narazil Amazon Rekognition. Po chv\\u00ed\\u013eke h\\u013eadania a\\u00a0bl\\u00fadenia o\\u00a0\\u010do vlastne ide, som narazil na celkom jednoduch\\u00fa defin\\u00edciu toho, ako vlastne Rekognition funguje. Ide o\\u00a0technol\\u00f3giu a\\u00a0dielne Amazon Web Services (AWS), ktor\\u00e1 poskytuje vysoko presn\\u00fa anal\\u00fdzu tv\\u00e1re a rozpozn\\u00e1vanie tv\\u00e1re na obr\\u00e1zkoch a vide\\u00e1ch, ktor\\u00e9 poskytujete. Amazon Rekognition je zalo\\u017een\\u00fd na vysoko \\u0161k\\u00e1lovate\\u013enej technol\\u00f3gii schopnej u\\u010di\\u0165 sa, ktor\\u00fa vyvinuli vedci z\\u00a0Amazonu. Na z\\u00e1klade anal\\u00fdz mili\\u00e1rd obr\\u00e1zkov a vide\\u00ed denne nevy\\u017eaduje sk\\u00fasenosti a\\u00a0expert\\u00edzu s\\u00a0machine learning syst\\u00e9mami.Tu sa v\\u0161ak pr\\u00edbeh nekon\\u010d\\u00ed. Magaz\\u00edn Forbes sa toti\\u017e rozhodol toto rie\\u0161enie otestova\\u0165. Zistil ve\\u013emi zauj\\u00edmav\\u00e9 veci, a\\u00a0teda \\u017ee okrem ve\\u013emi lacn\\u00e9ho rie\\u0161enia ide aj o\\u00a0rie\\u0161enie extr\\u00e9mne presn\\u00e9. Na z\\u00e1klade fotografi\\u00ed dobrovo\\u013ene poskytnut\\u00fdch od zamestnancov v\\u00a0kancel\\u00e1ri\\u00e1ch v Jersey a\\u00a0v\\u00a0Lond\\u00fdne, bol t\\u00edm \\u013eud\\u00ed okolo Thomasa Fox-Brewstera schopn\\u00fd po nieko\\u013ek\\u00fdch hodin\\u00e1ch postavi\\u0165 extr\\u00e9mne presn\\u00e9 rie\\u0161enie na rozpoznanie tv\\u00e1r\\u00ed.Prv\\u00fdm krokom bolo nastavenie AWS datab\\u00e1zy \\u2013 \\u201eS3 bucket\\u201c, do ktorej t\\u00edm nahral r\\u00f4zne n\\u00e1hodn\\u00e9 fotografie spolu s\\u00a0fotkami (t\\u00fdmi v\\u00a0\\u0161t\\u00fdle krimin\\u00e1lka Las Vegas) svojich zamestnancov. Rekognition nem\\u00e1 jednoduch\\u00fd n\\u00e1stroj na vizualiz\\u00e1ciu a\\u00a0sp\\u00e1rovanie tv\\u00e1re, ktor\\u00e9ho v\\u00fdsledkom je textov\\u00fd output. Preto bol s\\u00a0nezi\\u0161tnou pomocou nez\\u00e1visl\\u00e9ho program\\u00e1tora nak\\u00f3den\\u00fd jednoduch\\u00fd skript, ktor\\u00fd ozna\\u010doval zelen\\u00fdm \\u0161tvor\\u010dekom okolo tv\\u00e1re \\u013eud\\u00ed, ktor\\u00ed v\\u00a0datab\\u00e1ze neboli a\\u00a0\\u010derven\\u00fdm \\u0161tvor\\u010dekom t\\u00fdch, ktor\\u00ed sa v\\u00a0datab\\u00e1ze nach\\u00e1dzali. Na to, aby mohol Rekognition porovn\\u00e1va\\u0165 tv\\u00e1re s\\u00a0datab\\u00e1zy bol nahran\\u00fd \\u201efake\\u201c z\\u00e1znam, ktor\\u00fd simuloval z\\u00e1bery z\\u00a0CCTV kamier.Na z\\u00e1klade inform\\u00e1ci\\u00ed, ktor\\u00e9 Thomas poskytol vo svojom \\u010dl\\u00e1nku, boli v\\u00fdsledky prekvapiv\\u00e9 nie len svojou presnos\\u0165ou, ale aj r\\u00fdchlos\\u0165ou odozvy. No \\u010do je e\\u0161te pozoruhodnej\\u0161ie je cena rie\\u0161enia od AWS pre rie\\u0161enie tejto ve\\u013ekosti, ktor\\u00e1 by pod\\u013ea zverejnen\\u00fdch inform\\u00e1ci\\u00ed nepresiahla 10$.<\\/p>","fulltext":"","state":1,"catid":"14","created":"2018-11-28 14:06:49","created_by":"558","created_by_alias":"","modified":"2018-11-28 14:06:49","modified_by":null,"checked_out":null,"checked_out_time":null,"publish_up":"2018-11-28 14:06:49","publish_down":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","images":"{\\"image_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"float_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_caption\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"float_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_caption\\":\\"\\"}","urls":"{\\"urla\\":false,\\"urlatext\\":\\"\\",\\"targeta\\":\\"\\",\\"urlb\\":false,\\"urlbtext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetb\\":\\"\\",\\"urlc\\":false,\\"urlctext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetc\\":\\"\\"}","attribs":"{\\"article_layout\\":\\"\\",\\"show_title\\":\\"\\",\\"link_titles\\":\\"\\",\\"show_tags\\":\\"\\",\\"show_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"info_block_position\\":\\"\\",\\"info_block_show_title\\":\\"\\",\\"show_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_associations\\":\\"\\",\\"show_author\\":\\"\\",\\"link_author\\":\\"\\",\\"show_create_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_modify_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_publish_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_item_navigation\\":\\"\\",\\"show_icons\\":\\"\\",\\"show_print_icon\\":\\"\\",\\"show_email_icon\\":\\"\\",\\"show_vote\\":\\"\\",\\"show_hits\\":\\"\\",\\"show_noauth\\":\\"\\",\\"urls_position\\":