(460, 37, 1, '', '2018-11-30 14:42:10', 558, 7109, '3479638589a49388991cc39ad871d7835b6135c1', '{"id":37,"asset_id":"252","title":"Vlastn\\u00e1 IT infra\\u0161trukt\\u00fara alebo cloudov\\u00e9 rie\\u0161enie - Ako si vybra\\u0165?","alias":"vlastna-it-infrastruktura-alebo-cloudove-riesenie-ako-si-vybrat","introtext":"<p>Ka\\u017ed\\u00e1 stredn\\u00e1 alebo ve\\u013ek\\u00e1 firma si ob\\u010das mus\\u00ed polo\\u017ei\\u0165 ot\\u00e1zku: \\u201eJe moja aplik\\u00e1cia, \\u010di produkt prev\\u00e1dzkovan\\u00e1 na vhodnej platforme?\\u201c Preto by sme v\\u00e1m chceli pribl\\u00ed\\u017ei\\u0165 z\\u00e1kladn\\u00e9 rozdiely medzi dostupn\\u00fdmi rie\\u0161niami, ich v\\u00fdhody, \\u010di siln\\u00e9 str\\u00e1nky a pom\\u00f4c\\u0165 tak pri rozhodovan\\u00ed.<\\/p>\\r\\n<h3 id=\\"ak\\u00e9-zmeny-prin\\u00e1\\u0161a-nov\\u00e9-nariadenie-v-oblasti-ochrany-osobn\\u00fdch-\\u00fadajov-ou-pre-firmy\\">1. Vlastn\\u00e9 fyzick\\u00e9 servery, \\u201cBare metal\\u201d<\\/h3>\\r\\n<p>Vlastni\\u0165 fyzick\\u00e9 servery, stara\\u0165 sa o ne, konfigurova\\u0165, plati\\u0165 za housing, elektrick\\u00fa energiu a cel\\u00e9 toto prostredie spravova\\u0165 a monitorova\\u0165 je hroziv\\u00e1 predstava pre mal\\u00e9 a stredn\\u00e9 firmy. Rie\\u0161en\\u00edm m\\u00f4\\u017ee by\\u0165 zazmluvnenie dod\\u00e1vate\\u013ea\\/spr\\u00e1vcu, \\u010do je zasa finan\\u010dne najn\\u00e1ro\\u010dnej\\u0161ie spomedzi pon\\u00fakan\\u00fdch mo\\u017enost\\u00ed. Kedy m\\u00e1 \\u201eBare metal\\u201c zmysel? D\\u00f4vody s\\u00fa pre niektor\\u00fdch tie slu\\u017eby, ktor\\u00e9 dok\\u00e1\\u017eu prev\\u00e1dzkova\\u0165 len slu\\u017ebou servovanou z bare metal platformy. Jedn\\u00e1 sa hlavne o bezpe\\u010dnos\\u0165 cel\\u00e9ho rie\\u0161enia, ku ktor\\u00e9mu nem\\u00e1 pr\\u00edstup nik, okrem spr\\u00e1vcu serverov a z\\u00e1kazn\\u00edka. K \\u010fal\\u0161iemu d\\u00f4vodu udr\\u017eova\\u0165 vlastn\\u00e9 fyzick\\u00e9 servery m\\u00f4\\u017ee by\\u0165 aj nariadenie GDPR, legislat\\u00edva a zmluvn\\u00e9 po\\u017eiadavky z\\u00e1kazn\\u00edkov, ktor\\u00e9 obmedzuj\\u00fa ukladanie d\\u00e1t mimo EU alebo do zdie\\u013eanej infra\\u0161trukt\\u00fary. V\\u0161etky tieto parametre ovplyv\\u0148uj\\u00fa v\\u00fdber vhodn\\u00e9ho rie\\u0161enia.<\\/p>\\r\\n<h3 id=\\"ak\\u00e9-konkr\\u00e9tne-z\\u00e1sady-alebo-princ\\u00edpy-ochrany-ou-nariadenie-prin\\u00e1\\u0161a-a-\\u010do-to-znamen\\u00e1-v-praxi\\">2. Priv\\u00e1tny cloud<\\/h3>\\r\\n<p>Podstatou poskytovania priv\\u00e1tneho cloudu je vytvori\\u0165 pre z\\u00e1kazn\\u00edkov dedikovan\\u00e9 prostredie na mieru, v ktorom je z\\u00e1kazn\\u00edk v \\u010do najv\\u00e4\\u010d\\u0161om mo\\u017enom rozsahu odseparovan\\u00fd od fyzickej platformy, na ktorej jeho produkt be\\u017e\\u00ed. V\\u00fdhody priv\\u00e1tneho cloudu s\\u00fa snaha cenovo konkurova\\u0165 verejn\\u00fdm cloudom a pritom pon\\u00faknu\\u0165 z\\u00e1kazn\\u00edkovi nie\\u010do navy\\u0161e. Z\\u00e1kazn\\u00edci ocenia aj podporu od technicky zdatn\\u00fdch administr\\u00e1torov dod\\u00e1vate\\u013ea, ktor\\u00ed vedia pom\\u00f4c\\u0165 pri h\\u013eadan\\u00ed probl\\u00e9mov aplik\\u00e1cie, vyladenie prostredia pre prev\\u00e1dzku datab\\u00e1zy alebo poradi\\u0165 vo veciach technickej implement\\u00e1cie produktu.<\\/p>\\r\\n<h3 id=\\"spom\\u00ednali-ste-technick\\u00e9-prostriedky-a-organiza\\u010dn\\u00e9-opatrenia-na-zaru\\u010denie-bezpe\\u010dnosti-sprac\\u00favania-osobn\\u00fdch-\\u00fadajov-vedeli-by-ste-uvies\\u0165-pr\\u00edklady-ako-zv\\u00fd\\u0161i\\u0165-bezpe\\u010dnos\\u0165\\">3. Verejn\\u00fd cloud<\\/h3>\\r\\n<p>V\\u00fdhody s\\u00fa v jasne nadefinovan\\u00fdch pravidl\\u00e1ch, a teda ak sa v tejto platforme nie\\u010do spravi\\u0165 d\\u00e1, tak to m\\u00f4\\u017eete spravi\\u0165 takmer okam\\u017eite p\\u00e1r klikmi my\\u0161ou vo webovom pou\\u017e\\u00edvate\\u013eskom rozhran\\u00ed cloudu. Ale to je aj nev\\u00fdhoda. Ak m\\u00e1 z\\u00e1kazn\\u00edk probl\\u00e9m a ten nie je technicky mo\\u017en\\u00e9 vyrie\\u0161i\\u0165 ohnut\\u00edm prostriedkov nadefinovan\\u00fdch poskytovate\\u013eom cez jeho webov\\u00fd interface, tak z\\u00e1kazn\\u00edk mus\\u00ed prisp\\u00f4sobi\\u0165 svoj produkt.<\\/p>\\r\\n<h3 id=\\"ak-nakoniec-d\\u00f4jde-k-incidentu-napr-k-strate-alebo-kr\\u00e1de\\u017ei-osobn\\u00fdch-\\u00fadajov-ak\\u00e9-kroky-s\\u00fa-potrebn\\u00e9-na-strane-prev\\u00e1dzkovate\\u013ea\\">Tak ako si m\\u00e1m vybra\\u0165?<\\/h3>\\r\\n<p>Ak ste dynamick\\u00fd a netrpezliv\\u00fd, potrebujete v\\u0161etko a hne\\u010f, tak sta\\u010d\\u00ed to, \\u010do poskytuje niektor\\u00fd verejn\\u00fd cloud. Ak u\\u017e m\\u00e1te produkt, ktor\\u00fd pon\\u00fakate a akt\\u00edvne ho vyv\\u00edjate a nevyhovuj\\u00fa v\\u00e1m obmedzenia ve\\u013ek\\u00fdch poskytovate\\u013eov alebo chcete \\u0165a\\u017ei\\u0165 zo spolupr\\u00e1ce administr\\u00e1torov, v\\u00fdvoj\\u00e1rov a z\\u00e1rove\\u0148 nechcete zbyto\\u010dne plati\\u0165 za spr\\u00e1vu vlastn\\u00e9ho hardv\\u00e9ru, tak vo\\u013eba je priv\\u00e1tny cloud. Ak nar\\u00e1bate s citliv\\u00fdmi d\\u00e1tami, po\\u017eadujete vysok\\u00fa \\u00farove\\u0148 bezpe\\u010dnosti alebo to legislat\\u00edva vy\\u017eaduje, vlastn\\u00fd fyzick\\u00fd server je rie\\u0161enie, \\u010do h\\u013ead\\u00e1m.Odpor\\u00fa\\u010dame sa, ale pred takouto zmenou poradi\\u0165 s odborn\\u00edkmi zo spolo\\u010dnosti Digmia a dohodn\\u00fa\\u0165 zdarma konzult\\u00e1ciu, kde v\\u00e1m poradia, ktor\\u00e9 rie\\u0161enie je pre v\\u00e1s najvhodnej\\u0161ie.<\\/p>","fulltext":"","state":1,"catid":"14","created":"2018-11-28 14:11:28","created_by":"558","created_by_alias":"","modified":"2018-11-30 14:42:10","modified_by":"558","checked_out":"558","checked_out_time":"2018-11-30 14:40:18","publish_up":"2018-11-28 14:11:28","publish_down":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","images":"{\\"image_intro\\":\\"images\\\\\\/clanky\\\\\\/620466077c427f141effa294382f5fba.jpg\\",\\"float_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_caption\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"float_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_caption\\":\\"\\"}","urls":"{\\"urla\\":false,\\"urlatext\\":\\"\\",\\"targeta\\":\\"\\",\\"urlb\\":false,\\"urlbtext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetb\\":\\"\\",\\"urlc\\":false,\\"urlctext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetc\\":\\"\\"}","attribs":"{\\"article_layout\\":\\"\\",\\"show_title\\":\\"\\",\\"link_titles\\":\\"\\",\\"show_tags\\":\\"\\",\\"show_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"info_block_position\\":\\"\\",\\"info_block_show_title\\":\\"\\",\\"show_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_associations\\":\\"\\",\\"show_author\\":\\"\\",\\"link_author\\":\\"\\",\\"show_create_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_modify_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_publish_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_item_navigation\\":\\"\\",\\"show_icons\\":\\"\\",\\"show_print_icon\\":\\"\\",\\"show_email_icon\\":\\"\\",\\"show_vote\\":\\"\\",\\"show_hits\\":\\"\\",\\"show_noauth\\":\\"\\",\\"urls_position\\":\\"\\",\\"alternative_readmore\\":\\"\\",\\"article_page_title\\":\\"\\",\\"show_publishing_options\\":\\"\\",\\"show_article_options\\":\\"\\",\\"show_urls_images_backend\\":\\"\\",\\"show_urls_images_frontend\\":\\"\\",\\"spfeatured_image\\":\\"\\",\\"post_format\\":\\"standard\\",\\"gallery\\":\\"\\",\\"audio\\":\\"\\",\\"video\\":\\"\\",\\"link_title\\":\\"\\",\\"link_url\\":\\"\\",\\"quote_text\\":\\"\\",\\"quote_author\\":\\"\\",\\"post_status\\":\\"\\"}","version":3,"ordering":"1","metakey":"","metadesc":"","access":"1","hits":"0","metadata":"{\\"robots\\":\\"\\",\\"author\\":\\"\\",\\"rights\\":\\"\\",\\"xreference\\":\\"\\"}","featured":"0","language":"sk-SK","xreference":"","note":""}', 0);
