(469, 33, 1, '', '2018-11-30 14:43:46', 558, 4828, '33b0f84a3c608d45633617d39463242ce69ab6c0', '{"id":33,"asset_id":"248","title":"Predn\\u00e1\\u0161ka o v\\u00fdvoj aplik\\u00e1ci\\u00ed","alias":"prednaska-o-vyvoj-aplikacii","introtext":"<h3 id=\\"ak\\u00e9-zmeny-prin\\u00e1\\u0161a-nov\\u00e9-nariadenie-v-oblasti-ochrany-osobn\\u00fdch-\\u00fadajov-ou-pre-firmy\\">V\\u00ddVOJI APLIK\\u00c1CI\\u00cd<\\/h3>\\r\\n<p>Na\\u0161i Senior Java Developeri Peter V\\u00e1vra a\\u00a0Filip \\u0160tiglic v\\u00a0r\\u00e1mci tejto predn\\u00e1\\u0161ky na dvoch stretnutiach za sebou v\\u00a0Univerzitnom pastora\\u010dnom centre v\\u00a0Bratislave objasnili, ak\\u00fdm smerom by sa mohol ubera\\u0165 v\\u00fdvoj aplik\\u00e1ci\\u00ed v\\u00a0t\\u00edme re\\u00e1lnej spolo\\u010dnosti a\\u00a0ak\\u00fd je rozdiel medzi ich v\\u00fdvojom na \\u0161kole a\\u00a0priamo v\\u00a0praxi \\u010di medzi r\\u00f4znymi spolo\\u010dnos\\u0165ami navz\\u00e1jom.V r\\u00e1mci ka\\u017edej t\\u00e9my podrobne vysvetlili dan\\u00e9 pojmy, ako aj ich vyu\\u017eitie v\\u00a0praxi. Tie\\u017e rozobrali, nako\\u013eko s\\u00fa jednotliv\\u00e9 t\\u00e9my d\\u00f4le\\u017eit\\u00e9 pre t\\u00edm, projekt, developera, testera \\u010di mana\\u017e\\u00e9ra. Peter a\\u00a0Filip tie\\u017e uk\\u00e1zali, ako to vyzer\\u00e1, ke\\u010f nie\\u010do rob\\u00edme zle \\u010di, naopak, spr\\u00e1vne a\\u00a0ak\\u00e9 to m\\u00f4\\u017ee ma\\u0165 re\\u00e1lne d\\u00f4sledky.V\\u010faka tomu maj\\u00fa absolventi tejto predn\\u00e1\\u0161ky preh\\u013ead o\\u00a0mo\\u017enostiach v\\u00fdvoja softv\\u00e9ru, ako aj o\\u00a0tom, kde nast\\u00e1vaj\\u00fa chyby. Nov\\u00e9 inform\\u00e1cie vyu\\u017eij\\u00fa v\\u0161ak aj inak \\u2013 v\\u010faka nim m\\u00f4\\u017eu napr\\u00edklad u\\u017e pri pohovore odhali\\u0165, do akej miery bude proces v\\u00fdvoja softv\\u00e9ru v\\u00a0novej firme pote\\u0161en\\u00edm alebo utrpen\\u00edm.Na\\u0161i \\u0161pecialisti na praktick\\u00fdch uk\\u00e1\\u017ekach tie\\