(492, 40, 1, '', '2018-12-05 14:08:08', 558, 12832, '7bc12e5038f8822376a4c290a32178737690ced6', '{"id":40,"asset_id":"255","title":"Najlep\\u0161ie cloudov\\u00e9 \\u00falo\\u017eiska pre va\\u0161e s\\u00fabory","alias":"najlepsie-cloudove-uloziska-pre-vase-subory","introtext":"<p>\\u00dalo\\u017en\\u00e9ho priestoru nikdy nie je dos\\u0165. Aj ke\\u010f kapacitu po\\u010d\\u00edta\\u010da dok\\u00e1\\u017eeme jednoducho roz\\u0161\\u00edri\\u0165 prostredn\\u00edctvom intern\\u00fdch, extern\\u00fdch diskov \\u010di USB k\\u013e\\u00fa\\u010dov s \\u010doraz v\\u00e4\\u010d\\u0161ou kapacitou, tak ako popul\\u00e1rnej\\u0161ia alternat\\u00edva sa dnes jav\\u00ed cloud, ktor\\u00fd pon\\u00faka d\\u00e1ta nez\\u00e1visle na platforme a jednoduch\\u00e9 mo\\u017enosti zdie\\u013eania, hoci vo v\\u00e4\\u010d\\u0161ine pr\\u00edpadov na \\u00fakor straty s\\u00fakromia. Oproti fyzick\\u00fdm nosi\\u010dom d\\u00e1t pon\\u00faka cloud viacero v\\u00fdhod. Nemus\\u00edme sa b\\u00e1\\u0165, \\u017ee o d\\u00e1ta pr\\u00eddeme chybou fyzick\\u00e9ho m\\u00e9dia, no hlavne k nim m\\u00e1me pr\\u00edstup odkia\\u013eko\\u013evek a z ak\\u00e9hoko\\u013evek zariadenia v pr\\u00edpade, \\u017ee m\\u00e1me dostato\\u010dne r\\u00fdchle a stabiln\\u00e9 pripojenie na internet. Ak si to okolnosti vy\\u017eaduj\\u00fa, jednotliv\\u00e9 d\\u00e1ta si dok\\u00e1\\u017eeme tie\\u017e stiahnu\\u0165 do zariadenia, aby sme k nim mali pr\\u00edstup, aj ke\\u010f nie sme pripojen\\u00fd na internet. Na v\\u00fdber m\\u00e1me zo \\u0161irok\\u00e9ho portf\\u00f3lia cloudov\\u00fdch rie\\u0161en\\u00ed a ka\\u017ed\\u00fd si m\\u00f4\\u017ee vybra\\u0165 pod\\u013ea svojich preferenci\\u00ed. Takmer ka\\u017ed\\u00e1 slu\\u017eba pon\\u00faka bezplatn\\u00fa verziu, no v pr\\u00edpade z\\u00e1ujmu o vy\\u0161\\u0161ie kapacity sa nevyhneme mesa\\u010dn\\u00fdm poplatkom.<\\/p>\\r\\n<h3 id=\\"ak\\u00e9-zmeny-prin\\u00e1\\u0161a-nov\\u00e9-nariadenie-v-oblasti-ochrany-osobn\\u00fdch-\\u00fadajov-ou-pre-firmy\\">Dropbox<\\/h3>\\r\\n<p>Dropbox je st\\u00e1licou na trhu cloudov\\u00fdch rie\\u0161en\\u00ed, ktor\\u00e1 sa vyzna\\u010duje jednoduchos\\u0165ou a spo\\u013eahlivos\\u0165ou. Pote\\u0161\\u00ed tie\\u017e jeho \\u0161irok\\u00e1 podpora a mo\\u017enos\\u0165 nain\\u0161talovania aplik\\u00e1cie na v\\u0161etky popul\\u00e1rne opera\\u010dn\\u00e9 syst\\u00e9my \\u010di u\\u017e na po\\u010d\\u00edta\\u010doch, alebo smartf\\u00f3noch. Aplik\\u00e1cie s\\u00fa ve\\u013emi dobre spracovan\\u00e9, s\\u00fa preh\\u013eadn\\u00e9 a umo\\u017e\\u0148uj\\u00fa jednoduch\\u00e9 a r\\u00fdchle zdie\\u013eanie s\\u00faborov. Spolo\\u010dnos\\u0165 tie\\u017e ned\\u00e1vno spustila slu\\u017ebu Paper, ktor\\u00e1 sl\\u00fa\\u017ei na tvorbu pozn\\u00e1mok \\u010di dokumentov a je priamo s Dropboxom prepojen\\u00e1.Hlavnou nev\\u00fdhodou Dropboxu je mal\\u00e1 ve\\u013ekos\\u0165 \\u00falo\\u017eiska v bezplatnej verzii. Ak nechcete plati\\u0165, po\\u010d\\u00edtajte len s 2 GB priestoru. Za 9,99 eura mesa\\u010dne alebo 99 eur ro\\u010dne si m\\u00f4\\u017eete predplati\\u0165 1 TB vo\\u013en\\u00e9ho priestoru. Firma pon\\u00faka tie\\u017e rie\\u0161enia pre t\\u00edmy, kde je mo\\u017en\\u00e9 z\\u00edska\\u0165 od 15 eur na mesiac neobmedzen\\u00fd priestor. Je v\\u0161ak nutn\\u00e9 po\\u010d\\u00edta\\u0165 s t\\u00fdm, \\u017ee d\\u00e1ta s\\u00fa ulo\\u017een\\u00e9 aj v USA a neza\\u0161ifrovan\\u00e9.<\\/p>\\r\\n<h3 id=\\"ak\\u00e9-konkr\\u00e9tne-z\\u00e1sady-alebo-princ\\u00edpy-ochrany-ou-nariadenie-prin\\u00e1\\u0161a-a-\\u010do-to-znamen\\u00e1-v-praxi\\">Google Drive<\\/h3>\\r\\n<p>Ak u\\u017e m\\u00e1te Google konto, tak m\\u00e1te automaticky pr\\u00edstup aj do cloudov\\u00e9ho \\u00falo\\u017eiska Google Drive. Ke\\u010f\\u017ee ide o produkt Googlu, tak je Drive silne integrovan\\u00fd do v\\u00e4\\u010d\\u0161iny slu\\u017eieb, ktor\\u00e9 Google pon\\u00faka. Google dokumenty vytvoren\\u00e9 v slu\\u017eb\\u00e1ch Sheets, Docs, Slides s\\u00fa v\\u0161etky centr\\u00e1lne dostupn\\u00e9 cez Drive disk \\u010do z\\u013eah\\u010duje pou\\u017e\\u00edvate\\u013eovi ich mana\\u017ement a zdie\\u013eanie. Do slu\\u017eby si tie\\u017e jednoducho ulo\\u017e\\u00edte pr\\u00edlohy z Gmailu a pote\\u0161\\u00ed aj integr\\u00e1cia Google Photos. Drive zdie\\u013ea svoje \\u00falo\\u017eisko s Gmailom a aj d\\u00e1tami z v\\u00e1\\u0161ho Google Photos, tak\\u017ee dostupn\\u00e1 kapacita je delen\\u00e1 medzi v\\u0161etky slu\\u017eby.V bezplatnej verzii Google pon\\u00faka 15 GB priestoru pre va\\u0161e s\\u00fabory. Ak v\\u00e1m je 15 GB m\\u00e1lo, no z\\u00e1rove\\u0148 nepotrebujete cel\\u00fd terabajt, tak existuje mo\\u017enos\\u0165 predplati\\u0165 si 100GB \\u00falo\\u017eisko za 1,99 eura mesa\\u010dne, resp. 19,99 pri platbe vopred za cel\\u00fd rok. Jeden TB priestoru stoj\\u00ed 9,99 eura mesa\\u010dne alebo 99,99 eura ro\\u010dne. Najviac je mo\\u017en\\u00e9 predplati\\u0165 si 30 TB za 299,99 eura mesa\\u010dne. Samozrejmos\\u0165ou je tie\\u017e aplik\\u00e1cia pre Windows, macOS ako aj Android a iOS. Aj v tomto pr\\u00edpade s\\u00fa d\\u00e1ta ulo\\u017een\\u00e9 v USA a neza\\u0161ifrovan\\u00e9.<\\/p>\\r\\n<h3 id=\\"spom\\u00ednali-ste-technick\\u00e9-prostriedky-a-organiza\\u010dn\\u00e9-opatrenia-na-zaru\\u010denie-bezpe\\u010dnosti-sprac\\u00favania-osobn\\u00fdch-\\u00fadajov-vedeli-by-ste-uvies\\u0165-pr\\u00edklady-ako-zv\\u00fd\\u0161i\\u0165-bezpe\\u010dnos\\u0165\\">OneDrive<\\/h3>\\r\\n<p>Vlastn\\u00e9 softv\\u00e9rov\\u00e9 \\u00falo\\u017eisko pon\\u00faka aj softv\\u00e9rov\\u00fd gigant Microsoft. OneDrive je s\\u00fa\\u010das\\u0165ou najnov\\u0161ieho opera\\u010dn\\u00e9ho syst\\u00e9mu Windows 10, no nat\\u00edvna aplik\\u00e1cia je dostupn\\u00e1 aj pre OSX i mobiln\\u00e9 platformy Windows Phone, Android a iOS. OneDrive je dobr\\u00e1 vo\\u013eba ak preferujete aj ostatn\\u00e9 produkty Microsoftu, ke\\u010f\\u017ee nech\\u00fdba dobr\\u00e9 prepojenie s cloudov\\u00fdm kancel\\u00e1rskym bal\\u00edkom MS Office 365.V z\\u00e1klade Microsoft pon\\u00faka 5 GB bezplatn\\u00e9ho \\u00falo\\u017eiska a za 2 eur\\u00e1 mesa\\u010dne je mo\\u017en\\u00e9 predplati\\u0165 si 50 GB cloudov\\u00e9ho priestoru. Nech\\u00fdba ani mo\\u017enos\\u0165 predplati\\u0165 si 1 TB rie\\u0161enie za 7 eur mesa\\u010dne, resp. 69 eur ro\\u010dne, pri\\u010dom v tomto bal\\u00edku sa nach\\u00e1dza licencia na slu\\u017eby MS Office 365. Znovu, d\\u00e1ta s\\u00fa ulo\\u017een\\u00e9 aj v USA a neza\\u0161ifrovan\\u00e9.<\\/p>\\r\\n<h3 id=\\"ak-nakoniec-d\\u00f4jde-k-incidentu-napr-k-strate-alebo-kr\\u00e1de\\u017ei-osobn\\u00fdch-\\u00fadajov-ak\\u00e9-kroky-s\\u00fa-potrebn\\u00e9-na-strane-prev\\u00e1dzkovate\\u013ea\\">iCloud<\\/h3>\\r\\n<p>Pou\\u017e\\u00edvatelia platformy Apple maj\\u00fa mo\\u017enos\\u0165 pou\\u017e\\u00edva\\u0165 iCloud, ktor\\u00fd je priamo integrovan\\u00fd do syst\\u00e9mov macOS a iOS. V\\u00fdhoda iCloudu sa prejav\\u00ed najm\\u00e4 vtedy ak vlastn\\u00edte viacero zariaden\\u00ed od Apple a prostredn\\u00edctvom iCloudu dok\\u00e1\\u017eete \\u013eahko synchronizova\\u0165 d\\u00e1ta medzi nimi. Kompatibilita s ostatn\\u00fdmi platformami je v\\u0161ak u\\u017e hor\\u0161ia.Aj Apple d\\u00e1va v z\\u00e1kladnom bal\\u00edku 5 GB \\u00falo\\u017eisko pre bezplatn\\u00e9 pou\\u017e\\u00edvanie a u\\u017e za 99 centov mesa\\u010dne je mo\\u017en\\u00e9 vyu\\u017e\\u00edva\\u0165 50GB \\u00falo\\u017eisko. \\u010ealej je v ponuke 200 GB za 2,99 eura mesa\\u010dne a 2 TB za 9,99 eura mesa\\u010dne. D\\u00e1ta s\\u00fa ulo\\u017een\\u00e9 v USA a len \\u010das\\u0165 je za\\u0161ifrovan\\u00e1.<\\/p>\\r\\n<h3 id=\\"nov\\u00e9-nariadenie-nadob\\u00fada-\\u00fa\\u010dinnos\\u0165-2552018-ako-s\\u00fa-podnikatelia-a-in\\u0161tit\\u00facie-pripraven\\u00e9-a-\\u010do-je-potrebn\\u00e9-urobi\\u0165-aby-dosiahli-s\\u00falad-s-t\\u00fdmto-nariaden\\u00edm\\">Mega<\\/h3>\\r\\n<p>Pre t\\u00fdch, ktor\\u00ed chc\\u00fa \\u010do najv\\u00e4\\u010d\\u0161ie \\u00falo\\u017eisko u\\u017e v bezplatnej verzii je vhodn\\u00e1 slu\\u017eba Mega, za ktorou stoj\\u00ed Kim Dotcom, autor u\\u017e kontroverzne zru\\u0161enej slu\\u017eby Megaupload. V bezplatnej verzii pon\\u00faka Mega pou\\u017e\\u00edvate\\u013eovi a\\u017e 50 GB d\\u00e1t. Pritom slu\\u017ebe nech\\u00fdbaj\\u00fa bohat\\u00e9 mo\\u017enosti synchroniz\\u00e1cie, aplik\\u00e1cie pre Windows, macOS a Linux, ako aj verzie pre mobiln\\u00e9 opera\\u010dn\\u00e9 syst\\u00e9my.Megu tie\\u017e m\\u00f4\\u017eete pou\\u017e\\u00edva\\u0165 ako roz\\u0161\\u00edrenie pre Chrome a Firefox. Mega je jedin\\u00e1 v tomto \\u010dl\\u00e1nku spom\\u00ednan\\u00e1 slu\\u017eba, ktor\\u00e1 m\\u00e1 d\\u00e1ta na svojich serveroch za\\u0161ifrovan\\u00e9 k\\u013e\\u00fa\\u010dmi, ktor\\u00e9 m\\u00e1te len vy ako vlastn\\u00edci d\\u00e1t. Slu\\u017eba Mega nevie, ak\\u00e9 d\\u00e1ta m\\u00e1te v cloude a d\\u00e1 sa pova\\u017eova\\u0165 za jedin\\u00fa, ktor\\u00e1 nenar\\u00fa\\u0161a va\\u0161e s\\u00fakromie.Ak by v\\u00e1m 50 GB nesta\\u010dilo, tak za 4,99 eura mesa\\u010dne je mo\\u017en\\u00e9 zak\\u00fapi\\u0165 si 200 GB priestoru, pri\\u010dom 1 TB stoj\\u00ed podobne ako pri konkurencii 9,99 eura. V ponuke s\\u00fa tie\\u017e 4 a 8 TB priestoru.<\\/p>\\r\\n<h3 id=\\"nov\\u00e9-nariadenie-nadob\\u00fada-\\u00fa\\u010dinnos\\u0165-2552018-ako-s\\u00fa-podnikatelia-a-in\\u0161tit\\u00facie-pripraven\\u00e9-a-\\u010do-je-potrebn\\u00e9-urobi\\u0165-aby-dosiahli-s\\u00falad-s-t\\u00fdmto-nariaden\\u00edm\\">Box<\\/h3>\\r\\n<p>Cloudov\\u00e9 \\u00falo\\u017eisko Box sa sna\\u017e\\u00ed cieli\\u0165 hlavne na firmy a firemn\\u00fdch pou\\u017e\\u00edvate\\u013eov, no oslovi\\u0165 m\\u00f4\\u017ee aj jednotlivcov. Slu\\u017eba pon\\u00faka takisto aplik\\u00e1cie pre v\\u0161etky hlavn\\u00e9 opera\\u010dn\\u00e9 syst\\u00e9my a navy\\u0161e pote\\u0161\\u00ed aj integr\\u00e1cia s mno\\u017estvom \\u010fal\\u0161\\u00edch slu\\u017eieb a aplik\\u00e1ci\\u00ed. Box tie\\u017e d\\u00e1va pou\\u017e\\u00edvate\\u013eovi mno\\u017estvo kontroly, \\u010do sa t\\u00fdka s\\u00fakromia.Bezplatn\\u00e9 \\u00falo\\u017eisko pon\\u00fakne pou\\u017e\\u00edvate\\u013eovi 10 GB priestoru a za 8 eur mesa\\u010dne je mo\\u017en\\u00e9 predplati\\u0165 si 100 GB, \\u010do je o nie\\u010do vy\\u0161\\u0161ia cena v porovnan\\u00ed s konkurenciou.<\\/p>\\r\\n<h3 id=\\"nov\\u00e9-nariadenie-nadob\\u00fada-\\u00fa\\u010dinnos\\u0165-2552018-ako-s\\u00fa-podnikatelia-a-in\\u0161tit\\u00facie-pripraven\\u00e9-a-\\u010do-je-potrebn\\u00e9-urobi\\u0165-aby-dosiahli-s\\u00falad-s-t\\u00fdmto-nariaden\\u00edm\\">Vlastn\\u00fd Cloud<\\/h3>\\r\\n<p>Jednou z mo\\u017enost\\u00ed je tie\\u017e zriadenie si vlastn\\u00e9ho cloudu. Popul\\u00e1rne s\\u00fa napr\\u00edklad rie\\u0161enia od spolo\\u010dnosti Synology. Sta\\u010d\\u00ed si zak\\u00fapi\\u0165 zariadenie NAS s kapacitou diskov, ak\\u00fa preferujete a n\\u00e1sledne u\\u017e za prev\\u00e1dzku neplat\\u00edte, ako je to v pr\\u00edpade \\u0161tandardn\\u00fdch cloudov\\u00fdch slu\\u017eieb. V\\u00fdhodou vlastn\\u00e9ho rie\\u0161enia je, \\u017ee presne viete kde sa va\\u0161e d\\u00e1ta nach\\u00e1dzaj\\u00fa a m\\u00e1te zaru\\u010den\\u00e9 s\\u00fakromie.Ani v pr\\u00edpade dom\\u00e1cich rie\\u0161en\\u00ed nech\\u00fdbaj\\u00fa mo\\u017enosti pr\\u00edstupu z viacer\\u00fdch zariaden\\u00ed \\u010di automatick\\u00e9 z\\u00e1lohovanie fotiek a n\\u00e1jdeme tie\\u017e obdoby slu\\u017eieb Sheets, Docs \\u010di \\u010fal\\u0161\\u00edch. Do ur\\u010ditej miery nech\\u00fdba ani prepojenos\\u0165 s cloudom zn\\u00e1mych hr\\u00e1\\u010dov na trhu.<\\/p>","fulltext":"","state":1,"catid":"16","created":"2018-11-28 14:12:45","created_by":"558","created_by_alias":"","modified":"2018-12-05 14:08:08","modified_by":"558","checked_out":"558","checked_out_time":"2018-12-05 14:06:49","publish_up":"2018-11-28 14:12:45","publish_down":"0000-00-00 00:00:0