(551, 54, 1, '', '2018-12-05 19:33:20', 558, 4172, '9017e3b2a1c9599c1e1c92bc5e5ab695a96c1353', '{"id":54,"asset_id":315,"title":"Lecture on application development","alias":"lecture-on-application-development","introtext":"<p>&lt;h3&gt;Application Development&lt;\\/h3&gt;<br \\/>&lt;p&gt;Our Senior Java Developers, Peter V\\u00e1vra and Filip \\u0160tiglic, in two lectures at the University Pastoral Center in Bratislava, explained in what way the development of applications in the real-world team could take place and what is the difference between their development at school and directly in practice or between different societies. Within each subject, they explain in detail the given terms as well as their use in practice. They also divorced because the individual topics are important for the project, the developer, the tester or the manager. Peter and Philip also showed what it looks like when we do something wrong or, on the contrary, the right thing and how it can have real consequences. Thanks to this, the lecturers of this lecture have an overview of the possibilities of software development as well as where the errors occur. However, the new information will also be used in other ways - for example, they can reveal the extent to which the process of software development in the new company will be a pleasure or suffering in the new company. Our practitioners also explained students to concepts such as:&lt;\\/p&gt;<br \\/>&lt;ul&gt;<br \\/>&lt;li&gt;Issue Tracking System - a software application that allows you to track the progress of each task&lt;\\/li&gt;<br \\/>&lt;li&gt;Architecture Design Tools - tools used to create a design,&lt;\\/li&gt;<br \\/>&lt;li&gt;versioning tools - application development tools,&lt;\\/li&gt;<br \\/>&lt;li&gt;building tools - tools for building applications,&lt;\\/li&gt;<br \\/>&lt;li&gt;Continuous Integration - Software that takes care of integration and ongoing system updates several times a day,&lt;\\/li&gt;<br \\/>&lt;li&gt;Migration - data transfer between two systems or alignment of changes during development,&lt;\\/li&gt;<br \\/>&lt;li&gt;logging - logging data for analysis,&lt;\\/li&gt;<br \\/>&lt;li&gt;environment&lt;\\/li&gt;<br \\/>&lt;li&gt;tests.&lt;\\/li&gt;<br \\/>&lt;li&gt;database&lt;\\/li&gt;<br \\/>&lt;li&gt;production.&lt;\\/li&gt;<br \\/>&lt;\\/ul&gt;<\\/p>","fulltext":"","state":1,"catid":"24","created":"2018-12-05 19:33:20","created_by":"558","created_by_alias":"","modified":"2018-12-05 19:33:20","modified_by":null,"checked_out":null,"checked_out_time":null,"publish_up":"2018-12-05 19:33:20","publish_down":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","images":"{\\"image_intro\\":\\"images\\\\\\/articles\\\\\\/22c02097e4438bd2f2f3fe4a6a3ab0e1.jpg\\",\\"float_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_caption\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"float_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_caption\\":\\"\\"}","urls":"{\\"urla\\":false,\\"urlatext\\":\\"\\",\\"targeta\\":\\"\\",\\"urlb\\":false,\\"urlbtext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetb\\":\\"\\",\\"urlc\\":false,\\"urlctext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetc\\":\\"\\"}","attribs":"{\\"article_layout\\":\\"\\",\\"show_title\\":\\"\\",\\"link_titles\\":\\"\\",\\"show_tags\\":\\"\\",\\"show_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"info_block_position\\":\\"\\",\\"info_block_show_title\\":\\"\\",\\"show_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_associations\\":\\"\\",\\"show_author\\":\\"\\",\\"link_author\\":\\"\\",\\"show_create_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_modify_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_publish_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_item_navigation\\":\\"\\",\\"show_icons\\":\\"\\",\\"show_print_icon\\":\\"\\",\\"show_email_icon\\":\\"\\",\\"show_vote\\":\\"\\",\\"show_hits\\":\\"\\",\\"show_noauth\\":\\"\\",\\"urls_position\\":\\"\\",\\"alternative_readmore\\":\\"\\",\\"article_page_title\\":\\"\\",\\"show_publishing_options\\":\\"\\",\\"show_article_options\\":\\"\\",\\"show_urls_images_backend\\":\\"\\",\\"show_urls_images_frontend\\":\\"\\",\\"spfeatured_image\\":\\"\\",\\"post_format\\":\\"standard\\",\\"gallery\\":\\"\\",\\"audio\\":\\"\\",\\"video\\":\\"\\",\\"link_title\\":\\"\\",\\"link_url\\":\\"\\",\\"quote_text\\":\\"\\",\\"quote_author\\":\\"\\",\\"post_status\\":\\"\\"}","version":1,"ordering":null,"metakey":"","metadesc":"","access":"2","hits":null,"metadata":"{\\"robots\\":\\"\\",\\"author\\":\\"\\",\\"rights\\":\\"\\",\\"xreference\\":\\"\\"}","featured":"0","language":"en-GB","xreference":"","note":""}', 0),
(552, 55, 1, '', '2018-12-05 19:34:17', 558, 5841, 'b809ea1110171cb32e14653f4e5cdf2771c6d9c4', '{"id":55,"asset_id":316,"title":"Custom IT Infrastructure or Cloud Solution - How to Choose?","alias":"custom-it-infrastructure","introtext":"<p><span class=\\"tlid-translation translation\\" tabindex=\\"-1\\">&lt;p&gt; Every medium or large business must ask the question: \\"Is my application a product running on a suitable platform?\\" Therefore, we would like to bring you closer to the basic differences between the solutions available, their advantages and strengths, and help in deciding . &lt;\\/ p&gt;<br \\/>&lt;h3 id = \\"what-changes-brings-new-regulation-in-area-protection-personal-data-ou-pre-business\\"&gt; 1. Custom physical servers, \\"Bare metal\\" &lt;\\/ h3&gt;<br \\/>&lt;p&gt; Own physical servers, care for them, configure, pay for housing, electricity and the whole environment to manage and monitor is a horrific idea for small and medium businesses. The solution may be the contractor''s \\/ manager''s contract, which is the most costly among the options offered. When does Bare Metal have a meaning? Reasons are for some of those services that can only be operated by a service serviced from a bare metal platform. This is mainly about the security of the entire solution that no one has access to except the server and customer manager. For the sake of maintaining their own physical servers, the GDPR regulation, the legislation, and the contractual requirements of customers that restrict the storage of data outside the EU or shared infrastructure may be. All of these parameters affect the choice of a suitable solution. &lt;\\/ P&gt;<br \\/>&lt;h3 id = \\"what-specific-principles-or-principles-protection-ou-regulation-brings-and-what-to-mean-in-practice\\"&gt; 2. Private cloud &lt;\\/ h3&gt;<br \\/>&lt;p&gt; The essence of providing a private cloud is to create a custom-tailored environment for customers where the customer is as far as possible separated from the physical platform on which his product is running. The benefits of a private cloud are the effort to compete with the public cloud while offering the customer something extra. Customers will also appreciate support from technically sophisticated vendor administrators who can help you troubleshoot application problems, fine-tune the database environment, or advise on technical product implementation issues. &lt;\\/ P&gt;<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span class=\\"tlid-translation translation\\" tabindex=\\"-1\\">&lt;h3 id = \\"remember-you-technical-means-and-organizational-measures-to-guarantee-safety-processing-personal-data-know-by-you-give-examples-how-increase-safety\\"&gt; 3. Public Cloud &lt;\\/ h3&gt;<br \\/>&lt;p&gt; The benefits are in clearly defined rules, so if something is done on this platform, you can do it almost instantly with a few mouse clicks in the cloud web user interface. But that is also a disadvantage. If a customer has a problem and can not technically be solved by bending the resources defined by the provider through his web interface, the customer must customize their product. &lt;\\/ P&gt;<br \\/>&lt;h3 id = \\"if-end-of-the-incident-eg-to-lose-or-theft-personal-data-what-steps-are-needed-on-the-operator?\\"&gt; &lt;\\/ h3&gt;<br \\/>&lt;p&gt; If you''re dynamic and impatient, you need everything and right now, so just what some public cloud provides. If you already have a product that you offer and actively develop and do not meet major provider limitations or want to benefit from the collaboration of administrators, developers, and you do not want to pay unnecessarily for managing your own hardware, the choice is a private cloud. If you deal with sensitive data, you require a high level of security or that legislation requires that your own physical server is the solution I am looking for. We recommend, but before this change consult with Digmia experts and arrange a free consultation where you will advise which solution is for you most suitable. &lt;\\/ p&gt;<\\/span><\\/p>","fulltext":"","state":1,"catid":"23","created":"2018-12-05 19:34:17","created_by":"558","created_by_alias":"","modified":"2018-12-05 19:34:17","modified_by":null,"checked_out":null,"checked_out_time":null,"publish_up":"2018-12-05 19:34:17","publish_down":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","images":"{\\"image_intro\\":\\"images\\\\\\/articles\\\\\\/620466077c427f141effa294382f5fba.jpg\\",\\"float_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_caption\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"float_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_caption\\":\\"\\"}","urls":"{\\"urla\\":false,\\"urlatext\\":\\"\\",\\"targeta\\":\\"\\",\\"urlb\\":false,\\"urlbtext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetb\\":\\"\\",\\"urlc\\":false,\\"urlctext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetc\\":\\"\\"}","attribs":"{\\"article_layout\\":\\"\\",\\"show_title\\":\\"\\",\\"link_titles\\":\\"\\",\\"show_tags\\":\\"\\",\\"show_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"info_block_position\\":\\"\\",\\"info_block_show_title\\":\\"\\",\\"show_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_associations\\":\\"\\",\\"show_author\\":\\"\\",\\"link_author\\":\\"\\",\\"show_create_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_modify_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_publish_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_item_navigation\\":\\"\\",\\"show_icons\\":\\"\\",\\"show_print_icon\\":\\"\\",\\"show_email_icon\\":\\"\\",\\"show_vote\\":\\"\\",\\"show_hits\\":\\"\\",\\"show_noauth\\":\\"\\",\\"urls_position\\":\\"\\",\\"alternative_readmore\\":\\"\\",\\"article_page_title\\":\\"\\",\\"show_publishing_options\\":\\"\\",\\"show_article_options\\":\\"\\",\\"show_urls_images_backend\\":\\"\\",\\"show_urls_images_frontend\\":\\"\\",\\"spfeatured_image\\":\\"\\",\\"post_format\\":\\"standard\\",\\"gallery\\":\\"\\",\\"audio\\":\\"\\",\\"video\\":\\"\\",\\"link_title\\":\\"\\",\\"link_url\\":\\"\\",\\"quote_text\\":\\"\\",\\"quote_author\\":\\"\\",\\"post_status\\":\\"\\"}","version