(555, 54, 1, '', '2018-12-05 19:37:54', 558, 3973, '287c246e85ee4c461801263ab5816db2d99985c7', '{"id":54,"asset_id":"315","title":"Lecture on application development","alias":"lecture-on-application-development","introtext":"<h3>Application Development<\\/h3>\\r\\n<p>Our Senior Java Developers, Peter V\\u00e1vra and Filip \\u0160tiglic, in two lectures at the University Pastoral Center in Bratislava, explained in what way the development of applications in the real-world team could take place and what is the difference between their development at school and directly in practice or between different societies. Within each subject, they explain in detail the given terms as well as their use in practice. They also divorced because the individual topics are important for the project, the developer, the tester or the manager. Peter and Philip also showed what it looks like when we do something wrong or, on the contrary, the right thing and how it can have real consequences. Thanks to this, the lecturers of this lecture have an overview of the possibilities of software development as well as where the errors occur. However, the new information will also be used in other ways - for example, they can reveal the extent to which the process of software development in the new company will be a pleasure or suffering in the new company. Our practitioners also explained students to concepts such as:<\\/p>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li>Issue Tracking System - a software application that allows you to track the progress of each task<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Architecture Design Tools - tools used to create a design,<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>versioning tools - application development tools,<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>building tools - tools for building applications,<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Continuous Integration - Software that takes care of integration and ongoing system updates several times a day,<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Migration - data transfer between two systems or alignment of changes during development,<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>logging - logging data for analysis,<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>environment<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>tests.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>database<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>production.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>","fulltext":"","state":1,"catid":"24","created":"2018-12-05 19:33:20","created_by":"558","created_by_alias":"","modified":"2018-12-05 19:37:54","modified_by":"558","checked_out":"558","checked_out_time":"2018-12-05 19:37:27","publish_up":"2018-12-05 19:33:20","publish_down":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","images":"{\\"image_intro\\":\\"images\\\\\\/articles\\\\\\/22c02097e4438bd2f2f3fe4a6a3ab0e1.jpg\\",\\"float_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_caption\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"float_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_caption\\":\\"\\"}","urls":"{\\"urla\\":false,\\"urlatext\\":\\"\\",\\"targeta\\":\\"\\",\\"urlb\\":false,\\"urlbtext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetb\\":\\"\\",\\"urlc\\":false,\\"urlctext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetc\\":\\"\\"}","attribs":"{\\"article_layout\\":\\"\\",\\"show_title\\":\\"\\",\\"link_titles\\":\\"\\",\\"show_tags\\":\\"\\",\\"show_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"info_block_position\\":\\"\\",\\"info_block_show_title\\":\\"\\",\\"show_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_associations\\":\\"\\",\\"show_author\\":\\"\\",\\"link_author\\":\\"\\",\\"show_create_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_modify_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_publish_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_item_navigation\\":\\"\\",\\"show_icons\\":\\"\\",\\"show_print_icon\\":\\"\\",\\"show_email_icon\\":\\"\\",\\"show_vote\\":\\"\\",\\"show_hits\\":\\"\\",\\"show_noauth\\":\\"\\",\\"urls_position\\":\\"\\",\\"alternative_readmore\\":\\"\\",\\"article_page_title\\":\\"\\",\\"show_publishing_options\\":\\"\\",\\"show_article_options\\":\\"\\",\\"show_urls_images_backend\\":\\"\\",\\"show_urls_images_frontend\\":\\"\\",\\"spfeatured_image\\":\\"\\",\\"post_format\\":\\"standard\\",\\"gallery\\":\\"\\",\\"audio\\":\\"\\",\\"video\\":\\"\\"